text: Maximovka () is a rural locality (a village) in Miyakibashevsky Selsoviet, Miyakinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 2 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 26 km from Kirgiz-Miyaki, 23 km from Anyasevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Miyakinsky District
title: Maximovka
